MWB_DOpus v8.0 -- By Trevor Morris & Leo Davidson.
**************************************************

Magic Workbench Toolbar Icons and Backdrop Pictures for Directory Opus 5.5
(Useful for people not using Opus5 too -- they work great with ToolManager,
TinyMeter (MWB_DOpus7, at least), and similar programs which need little
brushes/icons).

@{" " LINK Contact} Who to contact with problems or suggestions.
@{" " LINK OldUser} Note for users DOpus 5.11 or MWB_DOpus v7.0.
@{" " LINK Contents} Contents of the archive.
@{" " LINK QandA} Quesions and Answers.

Sorry for the brevity of this document, it was written in a bit of
a hurry. Maybe in an update we'll have more hints and other intersting
stuff in the guide like we did in MWB_DOpus7...

      Leo 'Nudel' Davidson, London, 11-Aug-1996.

